data.description:
Call Direct  Dave

Don't miss seeing this high end home.  Wood Floors, Granite window sills, custom cabinetry and much more.  Theater room, 4 car garage with second high door to fit all of the toys/boat inside, 2 Living rooms, walk in safe/storage room with fireproof locking door, office with custom imported cherry wood, 5 bedrooms, 2 laundry rooms up and down, and more...
data.whatILove:
I love this house, it is centralized between SLC and Ogden and has all that you will need for grocery, shopping, restaurants, etc.  My commute to SLC is smooth and easy.  

The house rears to a church which provides privacy and openness.  

One of the highlights of this house is how safe the area is and the quality of amazing neighbors that are in this neighborhood.  We are surrounded by amazing people to call neighbors.

Davis County School District - 4 schools within walking distance of the house both charter and public schools.  Many children of all ages/parks nearby and more.  This is a great location.  

We love the suburb feel with the big city nearby!!!
